question.text: macam mana nak topup Tesla yg boss bagi yadi
variations: Tesla macam mana cara nak topup

languages.en: how to top up Tesla
languages.ms: macam mana nak topup Tesla

detailed.en:
To top up in Tesla, you can follow these steps: 

🔹 **ATM/Transfer (Min RM10)**
1️⃣ Use Instant Transfer or DuitNow (❌ Do not use IBG).
2️⃣ Enter the company account number and the amount you want to add.
3️⃣ Add your JOKER ID in 'Recipient Reference' (if using online banking).
4️⃣ Upload the receipt on the top-up page in the app.
5️⃣ Wait 3-10 minutes for processing.

🔹 **Fast Payment (FPX) (Min RM50, faster)**
1️⃣ Go to the top-up page in the app.
2️⃣ Select FPX and your bank.
3️⃣ Enter the amount and confirm the transaction.
4️⃣ Wait 1-3 minutes for automatic confirmation.

📌 Ensure the bank account name matches the name registered in the app. If you have any issues, just reply in the live chat!
detailed.ms:
Untuk top up di Tesla, anda boleh ikut langkah-langkah ini:

🔹 **ATM/Transfer (Min RM10)**
1️⃣ Gunakan Instant Transfer atau DuitNow (❌ Jangan gunakan IBG).
2️⃣ Masukkan nombor akaun syarikat dan jumlah yang ingin ditambah.
3️⃣ Tambahkan JOKER ID anda dalam 'Recipient Reference' (jika menggunakan perbankan dalam talian).
4️⃣ Muat naik resit di halaman top-up dalam aplikasi.
5️⃣ Tunggu 3-10 minit untuk proses.

🔹 **Fast Payment (FPX) (Min RM50, lebih cepat)**
1️⃣ Pergi ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi.
2️⃣ Pilih FPX dan bank anda.
3️⃣ Masukkan jumlah dan sahkan transaksi.
4️⃣ Tunggu 1-3 minit untuk pengesahan automatik.

📌 Pastikan nama akaun bank sepadan dengan nama yang didaftarkan dalam aplikasi. Jika ada sebarang masalah, balas saja dalam live chat ya!

question.text: What should I do if my Fast Payment (FPX) top-up doesn't reflect after 10 minutes?

languages.en: What should I do if my Fast Payment (FPX) top-up doesn't reflect after 10 minutes?

detailed.en:
To top up using an ATM, follow these steps:

1. Go to any bank ATM that supports interbank transfers.
2. Select the 'Transfer' or 'Money Transfer' menu.
3. Enter our company account number (refer to the top-up page in the app).
4. Enter the top-up amount (Minimum RM10).
5. Confirm the transaction and keep the receipt.
6. Take a picture of the receipt and upload it to the top-up page in the app, not in live chat.
7. The top-up will be processed within 3-10 minutes.

Make sure the receipt is clear and complete to avoid rejection.
If you have any issues or need assistance, please reply to us in live chat!
detailed.ms:

1. Pergi ke ATM mana-mana bank yang menyokong pemindahan antara bank.

3. Masukkan nombor akaun syarikat kami (rujuk halaman top-up dalam aplikasi).
4. Masukkan amaun top-up (Min RM10).
5. Sahkan transaksi dan simpan resit.
6. Ambil gambar resit dan muat naik ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, bukan dalam live chat.
7. Top-up akan diproses dalam 3-10 minit.

Pastikan resit jelas dan lengkap untuk mengelakkan penolakan.
Jika ada masalah atau perlukan bantuan, balas kami dalam live chat ya!

3. 输入我们的公司账户号码（请参阅应用程序中的充值页面）。
4. 输入充值金额（最低RM10）。
5. 确认交易并保留收据。
6. 拍摄收据的照片并上传到应用程序中的充值页面，而不是在实时聊天中。
7. 充值将在3-10分钟内处理。

确保收据清晰完整，以避免拒绝。

detailed.ms: Hai bos, kemenangan dari pertaruhan bola anda akan dikreditkan ke dalam dompet anda secara automatik dalam masa 24 jam pada hari yang sama. Sila bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses. Jika ia masih belum dikreditkan selepas 24 jam, anda boleh menghubungi kami melalui live chat untuk pengesahan. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: How can my friend join the Jokers? Please send the link.

languages.en: How can my friend join the Jokers? Please send the link.
languages.ms: Bagaimana kawan saya boleh sertai Jokers? Sila hantar pautan.
languages.cn: 我的朋友如何加入Jokers？请发送链接。

detailed.en: To register, your friend should follow these steps: 1. Go to 'Profile' in the app. 2. Copy the 'Referral Link' found in your profile. 3. Send that link to your friend for registration. 4. Your friend can use that link to register and start playing. The Referral Link is only available in your own account within the app. If there are any issues or if assistance is needed, please contact us via live chat.
detailed.ms: Untuk mendaftar, kawan anda perlu mengikuti langkah-langkah ini: 1. Pergi ke 'Profile' dalam aplikasi. 2. Salin 'Referral Link' yang terdapat dalam profil anda. 3. Hantar pautan tersebut kepada kawan anda untuk pendaftaran. 4. Kawan anda boleh menggunakan pautan tersebut untuk mendaftar dan mula bermain. Pautan Referral hanya boleh didapati dalam akaun anda sendiri dalam aplikasi. Jika ada sebarang masalah atau memerlukan bantuan, sila hubungi kami melalui live chat.
detailed.cn: 要注册，您的朋友应遵循以下步骤：1. 在应用程序中转到“个人资料”。2. 复制您个人资料中的“推荐链接”。3. 将该链接发送给您的朋友以进行注册。4. 您的朋友可以使用该链接进行注册并开始游戏。推荐链接仅在您自己的帐户中可用。如果有任何问题或需要帮助，请通过在线聊天与我们联系。

question.text: How long does it take for a credit to be reflected in my account after making a deposit?

languages.en: How long does it take for a credit to be reflected in my account after making a deposit?
languages.ms: Berapa lama masa yang diambil untuk kredit dipantulkan dalam akaun saya selepas membuat deposit?
languages.cn: 在我存款后，信用多久会反映在我的账户中？

detailed.en: If you have made a deposit of RM15 and it has not been credited to your wallet, please check the transaction receipt that you uploaded. Sometimes, deposits may experience delays due to certain terms or conditions. If you have checked and are still facing issues, please contact our customer support for further assistance. I hope this issue can be resolved quickly!
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah membuat deposit RM15 dan ia belum dikredit ke dalam wallet, sila semak semula resit transaksi yang telah dimuat naik. Kadang-kadang, deposit mungkin mengalami kelewatan disebabkan oleh terma atau syarat tertentu. Jika anda sudah semak dan masih menghadapi masalah, sila hubungi sokongan pelanggan kami untuk bantuan lanjut. Semoga masalah ini dapat diselesaikan segera!
detailed.cn: 如果您已经存入RM15，但尚未记入您的钱包，请检查您上传的交易收据。有时，存款可能会因某些条款或条件而延迟。如果您已经检查过并且仍然遇到问题，请联系客户支持以获得进一步的帮助。希望这个问题能尽快解决！

question.text: What should I do if my winnings from the 9pm Jaguar bet have not been credited to my account?

languages.en: What should I do if my winnings from the 9pm Jaguar bet have not been credited to my account?

detailed.en: If your winnings from the 9pm Jaguar bet have not been credited, it usually gets credited automatically to your wallet. Please check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM for confirmation. If your winnings still haven't been credited after that time, please contact live chat with a screenshot of your transaction for further verification. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan bet Jaguar 9pm anda belum dikreditkan, biasanya ia akan masuk secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Sila semak bahagian 'Report' antara 10:00 PM dan 10:30 PM untuk pengesahan. Jika selepas waktu tersebut kemenangan anda masih belum masuk, sila hubungi live chat dengan tangkapan skrin transaksi anda untuk pengesahan lanjut. Semoga berjaya!

question.text: I won the second prize at 9 PM, but why hasn't the money been credited to my account yet?

languages.en: I won the second prize at 9 PM, but why hasn't the money been credited to my account yet?
languages.ms: Saya menang hadiah kedua pada jam 9 malam, tetapi mengapa wang itu belum dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya?
languages.cn: 我在晚上9点赢得了二等奖，但为什么钱还没有进我的账户？

detailed.en: The winnings for J2 and J3 will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please be patient as the system is processing. You can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM to see the credit.
detailed.ms: Kemenangan untuk J2 dan J3 akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Sila bersabar ya, sistem sedang memproses. Anda boleh semak di bahagian 'Report' antara 10:00 PM hingga 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit tersebut.

question.text: What should I do if my prize winnings are not showing up?

detailed.ms: Jika anda mengalami kelewatan dalam menerima kemenangan anda, sila nyatakan sama ada ia dari 4D, bola, atau permainan lain supaya saya boleh membantu anda menyemak statusnya.
detailed.cn: 如果您在收到奖金方面遇到延迟，请说明是来自4D、球还是其他游戏，以便我可以帮助您检查状态。

question.text: What does it mean when the status shows PENDING in the system?

languages.en: What does it mean when the status shows PENDING in the system?
languages.ms: Apa maksudnya apabila status menunjukkan PENDING dalam sistem?
languages.cn: 当状态显示为PENDING时，这意味着什么？

detailed.en: When the status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing your request. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the status is still PENDING, you can contact live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Apabila status menunjukkan PENDING, ini bermakna sistem sedang memproses permintaan anda. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem menyelesaikan proses. Jangan muat naik resit berulang kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan status masih PENDING, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.
detailed.cn: 当状态显示为PENDING时，这意味着系统正在处理您的请求。请等待系统完成处理。请勿多次上传收据，因为这会减慢处理速度。如果超过10分钟状态仍为PENDING，您可以联系在线聊天以获取进一步帮助。

detailed.cn: 如果状态显示为PENDING，这意味着系统正在处理您的请求。请等待系统完成处理。请不要多次上传收据，因为这会减慢处理速度。如果超过10分钟状态仍然是PENDING，您可以联系在线聊天以获取进一步的帮助。

question.text: Can the 90 amount be credited to the wallet, and how does the deposit and bonus system work?

How does the deposit and bonus system work?

question.text: Can you provide guidance on how to submit a receipt photo correctly?

languages.en: Can you provide guidance on how to submit a receipt photo correctly?

detailed.en: Please make sure the uploaded receipt photo is complete and clear with the following details: 1️⃣ Successful – Make sure the transaction status shows as successful. 2️⃣ Amount – The exact transaction amount. 3️⃣ Date / Time – The accurate date and time of the transaction. 4️⃣ Recipient – The name of the recipient shown on the receipt. If the image is incomplete, kindly resubmit with a clear and full version, ya boss. Thank you so much! 🙏😊

question.text: I mistakenly uploaded the wrong receipt for my top-up. What should I do?
variations: I uploaded the wrong receipt
What to do if I made a mistake with my receipt?

languages.en: I mistakenly uploaded the wrong receipt for my top-up. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya silap muat naik resit untuk top-up saya. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?
languages.cn: 我错误地上传了我的充值收据。我该怎么办？

detailed.en: If you have submitted two receipts for the top-up, the system only requires one receipt for verification. Make sure not to upload the same receipt twice, as it may be rejected. Please wait 3-10 minutes for processing. If there are any issues, feel free to reply to us in the live chat.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah menghantar dua resit untuk top-up, sistem hanya memerlukan satu resit untuk semakan. Pastikan untuk tidak mengupload resit yang sama dua kali, kerana ia mungkin akan ditolak. Sila tunggu 3-10 minit untuk pemprosesan. Jika ada sebarang masalah, jangan ragu untuk balas kepada kami dalam live chat.
detailed.cn: 如果您提交了两张充值收据，系统只需要一张收据进行验证。请确保不要重复上传同一张收据，因为它可能会被拒绝。请等待3-10分钟进行处理。如果有任何问题，请随时在实时聊天中回复我们。

question.text: Apakah status pengkreditan dana untuk resit 9909 yang saya hantar?
variations: Kena ke resit 9909?
Bila dana akan dikreditkan untuk resit 9909?

detailed.ms: Kemenangan 4D akan dikreditkan ke wallet JOKER secara automatik. Mohon bersabar ya, sistem sedang memproses.

question.text: Bagaimana jika kemenangan J3 saya belum masuk dan saya sudah bank in RM33 tetapi masih tiada kemasukan?
variations: Kemenangan J3 saya belum masuk, apa yang perlu saya buat?
Saya sudah bank in tetapi tiada kemasukan, kenapa?

languages.ms: Bagaimana jika kemenangan J3 saya belum masuk dan saya sudah bank in RM33 tetapi masih tiada kemasukan?

detailed.en: If your J3 winnings have not been credited yet, please wait around 10 minutes for the system to process. If it still does not appear, contact live chat with your transaction details. If you have already banked in RM33 but it still hasn't been credited, there might be a slight delay. Please wait another 10 minutes. If it still does not appear, send a screenshot of the receipt to us via live chat so we can help resolve this issue.
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan J3 anda belum masuk, sila tunggu sekitar 10 minit untuk sistem memproses. Jika masih tidak muncul, sila hubungi live chat dengan butiran transaksi anda. Jika sudah bank in RM33 tetapi masih belum masuk, mungkin ada sedikit kelewatan. Sila tunggu sekitar 10 minit lagi. Jika masih tiada, hantar screenshot resit kepada kami melalui live chat supaya kami boleh bantu selesaikan masalah ini.

question.text: Can you confirm if the payment has been successfully processed and if the receipt is the same as the previous one?

languages.en: Can you confirm if the payment has been successfully processed and if the receipt is the same as the previous one?
languages.ms: Bolehkah anda mengesahkan jika pembayaran telah diproses dengan jayanya dan jika resit adalah sama seperti yang sebelumnya?
languages.cn: 您能确认付款是否已成功处理，并且收据是否与之前的相同吗？

detailed.en: Yes, the receipt this time is the same as the one uploaded earlier. Please check your wallet to confirm the payment.
detailed.ms: Ya, resit kali ini adalah sama dengan yang dimuat naik sebelum ini. Sila semak dompet anda untuk mengesahkan pembayaran.
detailed.cn: 是的，这次的收据与之前上传的相同。请检查您的钱包以确认付款。

question.text: How long does it take for my winnings to be credited to my wallet after winning in J3?

When will my J3 winnings appear in my wallet?

languages.en: How long does it take for my winnings to be credited to my wallet after winning in J3?
languages.ms: Berapa lama masa yang diambil untuk kemenangan saya dikreditkan ke dalam dompet selepas menang di J3?

detailed.en: Your J3 winnings will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please be patient as the system is processing. You can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM to see the credit. Thank you for your patience, and may you have a big win!
detailed.ms: Kemenangan J3 anda akan dikreditkan ke dalam dompet secara automatik. Sila bersabar ya, sistem sedang memproses. Anda boleh semak di bahagian 'Report' antara 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit tersebut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda, dan semoga anda dapat kemenangan besar!

question.text: What should I do if my winnings have not been credited to my account after a Jaguar bet?
variations: Why hasn't my Jaguar bet winnings been credited?
What is the process for winnings crediting?

languages.en: What should I do if my winnings have not been credited to my account after a Jaguar bet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya selepas pertaruhan Jaguar?

detailed.en: If your Jaguar bet winnings at 9 PM have not been credited, please wait between 10 to 30 minutes for the system to process. You can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM for the crediting. If you are using IBOX, the process may take a little longer. If after that period your winnings are still not credited, please contact live chat with a screenshot of your transaction for further verification. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan pertaruhan Jaguar anda pada jam 9 malam belum dikreditkan, sila tunggu antara 10 hingga 30 minit untuk sistem memproses. Anda boleh menyemak bahagian 'Laporan' antara 10:00 malam dan 10:30 malam untuk pengkreditan. Jika anda menggunakan IBOX, proses mungkin mengambil sedikit masa lebih lama. Jika selepas tempoh itu kemenangan anda masih belum dikreditkan, sila hubungi live chat dengan tangkapan skrin transaksi anda untuk pengesahan lanjut. Semoga berjaya!

question.text: What should I do if I mistakenly banked into the wrong account number?
variations: I made a mistake with my bank transfer.
I accidentally sent money to the wrong account.

languages.en: What should I do if I mistakenly banked into the wrong account number?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tersalah bank ke nombor akaun yang salah?

detailed.en: If you have transferred to your old bank account, unfortunately, the money cannot be refunded. However, you can still use the credited amount to play. You should ensure to top-up correctly by uploading your bank-in receipt through (WALLET → TOPUP). After submission, wait 3-10 minutes for the system to process the transaction. If the credit does not appear within 10 minutes, please contact live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah transfer ke akaun bank lama anda, malangnya, duit tersebut tidak dapat dipulangkan. Namun, anda masih boleh menggunakan amaun yang telah dikreditkan untuk bermain. Pastikan untuk top-up dengan betul dengan memuat naik resit bank-in anda melalui (WALLET → TOPUP). Selepas penghantaran, tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem memproses transaksi. Jika kredit tidak muncul dalam masa 10 minit, sila hubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if I accidentally entered the wrong bank account for a transfer?

languages.en: What should I do if I accidentally entered the wrong bank account for a transfer?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tersalah masukkan akaun bank untuk pemindahan?
languages.cn: 如果我不小心输入了错误的银行账户进行转账，我该怎么办？

detailed.en: If you accidentally transferred to your own bank account, the funds cannot be returned. However, you can still use the credited amount for gaming. Make sure to top-up correctly by uploading the bank-in slip through (WALLET → TOPUP). After submission, wait 3-10 minutes for the system to process the transaction. If the credit does not arrive within 10 minutes, please contact live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda tersalah transfer ke akaun bank sendiri, wang tersebut tidak dapat dikembalikan. Namun, anda masih boleh menggunakan jumlah yang telah dikreditkan untuk permainan. Pastikan untuk top-up dengan betul dengan memuat naik slip bank-in melalui (WALLET → TOPUP). Selepas penghantaran, tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem memproses transaksi. Jika kredit tidak tiba dalam 10 minit, sila hubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.
detailed.cn: 如果您不小心转账到自己的银行账户，资金是无法退回的。不过，您仍然可以使用已入账的金额进行游戏。请确保通过 (WALLET → TOPUP) 正确充值并上传银行存款单。提交后，请等待 3-10 分钟以便系统处理交易。如果在 10 分钟内未到账，请联系在线聊天以获取进一步帮助。

1. Go to any bank ATM that supports interbank transfers.
2. Select the 'Transfer' or 'Money Transfer' menu.
3. Enter our company account number (refer to the top-up page in the app).

If you have any issues or need assistance, reply to us in live chat!

4. Masukkan amaun top-up (Min RM10).

6. Ambil gambar resit dan muat naik ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, bukan dalam live chat.
